%% Diagram: Diagram 5
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant API
    participant Q as Queue
    participant Sg as DKIM
    participant MTA
    participant DNS
    participant Rc as Recipient

    C->>API: POST /send
    API->>API: validate
    API->>Q: enqueue
    API-->>C: 202 (id)
    Q->>Sg: sign DKIM
    Sg->>MTA: signed
    MTA->>DNS: MX
    DNS-->>MTA: mx record
    MTA->>Rc: SMTP
    alt Success
        Rc-->>MTA: 250 OK
        MTA->>Q: delivered
    else 4xx
        Rc-->>MTA: 421
        MTA->>Q: retry
    else 5xx
        Rc-->>MTA: 550
        MTA->>Q: bounce
    end
